---
// MultiModelShowcase: Two-column section with placeholder image on the left
// and headline + bullet points on the right, matching the dark theme.
---

<section class="py-20 bg-dark">
  <div class="container-custom">
    <div class="grid gap-10 lg:gap-16 lg:grid-cols-2 items-center">
      <!-- Left: Demo video -->
      <div class="relative order-2 lg:order-1">
        <div class="bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-xl max-w-[260px] sm:max-w-[320px] lg:max-w-[380px] mx-auto">
          <video
            src="/logo/0923.mov"
            class="w-full h-auto block"
            poster="/images/screenshot.png"
            preload="metadata"
            autoplay
            loop
            muted
            playsinline
          >
            Sorry, your browser doesn't support embedded videos.
          </video>
        </div>
        <!-- Glow accents -->
        <div class="pointer-events-none absolute -top-6 -left-6 w-40 h-40 bg-primary/30 blur-3xl rounded-full"></div>
        <div class="pointer-events-none absolute -bottom-8 -right-8 w-40 h-40 bg-secondary/30 blur-3xl rounded-full"></div>
      </div>

      <!-- Right: Copy -->
      <div class="order-1 lg:order-2">
        <div class="text-sm font-semibold text-primary mb-2">Multiple AI Models in a Single Chat</div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-extrabold leading-tight text-white">
          Start with GPT 5, Clarify with Claude Opus 4,
          <span class="block">Optimize with DeepSeek</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="text-gray-300 mt-2 italic">(without losing any context)</p>
        <p class="text-gray-300 mt-4">
          Many tools force you to restart when switching models. Astro AI keeps your full
          conversation history intact—even as you change AI engines—so you can mix strengths
          and get better outcomes.
        </p>

        <!-- Bulleted feature list -->
        <ul class="mt-6 space-y-4">
          <li class="flex gap-3">
            <span class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-white/10 border border-white/10 overflow-hidden">
              <img src="/logo/chat-gpt-logo-vector-black-3ded.png" alt="GPT 5 Logo" class="w-7 h-7 object-contain" loading="lazy" />
            </span>
            <div>
              <div class="text-white font-semibold">GPT 5</div>
              <div class="text-gray-400 text-sm">State‑of‑the‑art reasoning and generation across text, images, and tools.</div>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-3">
            <span class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-white/10 border border-white/10 overflow-hidden">
              <img src="/logo/claude-ai-icon-65aa.png" alt="Claude Opus 4 Logo" class="w-7 h-7 object-contain" loading="lazy" />
            </span>
            <div>
              <div class="text-white font-semibold">Claude Opus 4</div>
              <div class="text-gray-400 text-sm">Exceptional at complex reasoning, long‑context summarization, and clarity.</div>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-3">
            <span class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-white/10 border border-white/10 overflow-hidden">
              <img src="/logo/gemini.png" alt="Gemini Logo" class="w-7 h-7 object-contain" loading="lazy" />
            </span>
            <div>
              <div class="text-white font-semibold">Gemini 2.5 Pro</div>
              <div class="text-gray-400 text-sm">Great for code understanding, debugging, and multimodal analysis.</div>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-3">
            <span class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-white/10 border border-white/10 overflow-hidden">
              <img src="/logo/deep-seek-logo-whale-1ced.png" alt="DeepSeek Logo" class="w-7 h-7 object-contain" loading="lazy" />
            </span>
            <div>
              <div class="text-white font-semibold">DeepSeek</div>
              <div class="text-gray-400 text-sm">Strong long‑form writing, step‑by‑step reasoning, and structure.</div>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-3">
            <span class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-white/10 border border-white/10 overflow-hidden">
              <img src="/logo/Perplexity-Emblem.png" alt="Perplexity Logo" class="w-7 h-7 object-contain" loading="lazy" />
            </span>
            <div>
              <div class="text-white font-semibold">Perplexity</div>
              <div class="text-gray-400 text-sm">Real‑time web research with citations and concise summaries.</div>
            </div>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
